Package com.rcsexample.basnlib

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BluetoothConnectionService.BluetoothConnectionListener
    Classes that implement this interface and register as a listener will have the callback methods called.
    DataFileReader.DataFileReaderListener  
    DataProvider.OnDataAvailableListener
    Classes that implement this interface and register as a listener (see DataProvider.registerListener(OnDataAvailableListener)) will be able to receive Data objects with this method.
    PacketDecoder.OnPacketDecodedListener
    Classes that implement this interface and register as a listener (see PacketDecoder.registerListener(OnPacketDecodedListener)) will be able to receive Packet objects and possible decoding errors with this method.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BluetoothConnectionService
    This class is designed to handle the connection with the Bluetooth sensor.
    ControlPacket
    This class is for sending 'Control command packages' to the bluetooth sensor.
    Data
    Data is a class designed to transfer a set of data points from various sources in a standardized way.
    DataFileReader  
    DataProvider
    This class is used to take care of various data sources and sends them in a unified way, using Data objects.
    DeviceListActivity
    This Activity appears as a dialog.
    Packet
    This class is designed to hold the information of a packet of data as sent from a InPriMo Activity Bluetooth sensor.
    PacketDecoder
    This class is used to cut a FIFO of raw bytes into frames, that become Packets.
